00:15:37,503 --> 00:15:40,664
Lakukan saja.
Kau akan kesakitan di pagi hari.

254
00:15:43,373 --> 00:15:45,574
Langsung pulang.
Jangan memukul lagi.

255
00:15:45,574 --> 00:15:46,903
Aku bilang tidak.

256
00:15:47,773 --> 00:15:49,243
Hati-hati mengemudinya.

257
00:15:49,773 --> 00:15:50,844
Jalan.

258
00:15:58,853 --> 00:15:59,983
Nasi.

259
00:16:02,054 --> 00:16:03,694
Nanti rambutmu
akan masuk dalam makananmu.

260
00:16:03,694 --> 00:16:05,263
Pelan-pelanlah.

261
00:16:05,594 --> 00:16:08,893
Bagaimana dia tidak 
memperhatikannya?

262
00:16:08,893 --> 00:16:11,603
Dia tidak memperhatikan rambutmu?/
Benar.

263
00:16:11,733 --> 00:16:13,434
Tapi di klub yang agak gelap itu,...

264
00:16:13,434 --> 00:16:15,704
